data.description: This little charmer is move in ready with ample parking & space for boat/RV. Situated just a 1/2 mile from the picturesque Horseshoe Lake; plus, 2 miles from the boat launch, this prime location is perfect for the outdoor enthusiast. Featuring 3 beds & 2 baths, this home has been thoughtfully updated. Metal roof, hardie plank siding, double pane windows, new water heater & toilets, newer furnace & covered porches, list some of the upgrades to this home. Bright kitchen w/ breakfast bar & dining room. Primary bedroom hosts ensuite bath & walk-in closet. Fully fenced backyard. Additional storage w/ the 10'x10' outdoor metal shed. Quick commute to local amenities such as the post office, Costco, Home Depot, restaurants, parks & more.
